linux commands --

have you heard of .tar and to make a file zip

tar -cvf filename.tar sourcefilename

it will be archieved.. 

and to zip that tar file

gzip filename.tar.gz

it will zip the file means compress it

to unzip the file

gunzip filename.tar.gz

it will unzip the file

and to unarchieve the file 

tar -xvf filename.tar dir1/  -- means to a directory

